<article id="article" class="article "><header><h1 class="title" itemprop="headline">John McCain fights back</h1>

					<p class="dek">You'd never know it but before work, Sen. John McCain starts his day with chemo and radiation. McCain tells 60 Minutes that he feels more energetic and engaged because of his diagnosis</p>
		
    </header><div class="social sharebar_expanded inline-sharebar theme-light  location-top" data-component="sharebar">

